<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Executive IT — Cybersécurité & Identités</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap');

    :root {
      --navy: #0a192f;
      --gold: #c5a059;
      --slate: #64748b;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
      --shield: #1e40af;
      --danger: #b91c1c;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--navy); display: flex; }

    /* Sidebar Corporate */
    .sidebar { width: 280px; height: 100vh; background: var(--navy); color: white; position: sticky; top: 0; padding: 40px 0; }
    .logo { padding: 0 30px 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    .logo h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; }
    .logo span { color: var(--gold); font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; display: block; }

    .nav-item { padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; color: #cbd5e1; transition: 0.3s; border-left: 3px solid transparent; }
    .nav-item.active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: white; border-left-color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }

    /* Main */
    .main { flex: 1; padding: 60px; max-width: 1300px; }
    .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 40px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--navy); padding-bottom: 20px; }
    .header h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 32px; }

    /* Cyber Grid */
    .panel { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .panel-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-left: 3px solid var(--shield); padding-left: 15px; }

    .cyber-metrics { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .metric-card { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; }
    .metric-val { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); display: block; }
    .metric-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--slate); text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 5px; }

    /* Governance Table */
    .table-cyber { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    .table-cyber th { text-align: left; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--slate); padding: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); }
    .table-cyber td { padding: 15px 12px; font-size: 13px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

    .status-badge { padding: 4px 8px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .status-ok { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
    .status-warn { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }

    /* Technical Stack Footer */
    .stack-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 30px; }
    .stack-box { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .stack-box strong { color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 11px; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="sidebar">
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>Executive IT</h1>
      <span>Architecture & Gouvernance</span>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-item">Vue Stratégique</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Portefeuille Apps</div>
    <div class="nav-item">TRM — Risques</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Finance IT</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Conformité & Data</div>
    <div class="nav-item active">Cyber : IAM & Accès</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Sourcing & Vendors</div>
  </nav>

  <main class="main">
    <header class="header">
      <h2>Gouvernance des Identités (IAM)</h2>
      <div style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--slate);">SÉCURISATION DES ACCÈS CRITIQUES</div>
    </header>

    <div class="cyber-metrics">
      <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-val">98%</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Couverture MFA</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-val">100%</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Comptes Privilégiés (PAM)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-val">85%</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Adoption SSO</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-val">12ms</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Latence Auth (OIDC)</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-title">État de Déploiement des Protocoles</div>
      <table class="table-cyber">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Domaine de Sécurité</th>
            <th>Standard Utilisé</th>
            <th>Taux de Conformité</th>
            <th>Statut Critique</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Authentification Web</strong></td>
            <td>OIDC (OpenID Connect)</td>
            <td>92%</td>
            <td><span class="status-badge status-ok">Sécurisé</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Fédération d'Identités</strong></td>
            <td>SAML 2.0 / SSO</td>
            <td>78%</td>
            <td><span class="status-badge status-warn">En cours</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Comptes à Hauts Privilèges</strong></td>
            <td>PAM (Privileged Access)</td>
            <td>100%</td>
            <td><span class="status-badge status-ok">Maîtrisé</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Gestion du Cycle de Vie</strong></td>
            <td>IAM (Joiners / Leavers)</td>
            <td>65%</td>
            <td><span class="status-badge status-warn">À Optimiser</span></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="stack-grid">
      <div class="stack-box">
        <strong>Focus Technique : PAM & MFA</strong>
        La sécurisation des administrateurs est assurée par un coffre-fort numérique (PAM) avec rotation automatique des mots de passe. Le Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) est obligatoire pour tout accès distant.
      </div>
      <div class="stack-box">
        <strong>Modernisation des Flux : OIDC</strong>
        Le passage systématique au protocole OpenID Connect (OIDC) permet d'unifier l'expérience utilisateur via le SSO tout en renforçant la sécurité des jetons d'accès applicatifs.
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
